prompts.frontCover: A whimsical and humorous fantasy scene in a dreamy, ethereal art style. A cartoon-style couple, representing the man and woman from the photos, are joyfully snowboarding down a magical, fluffy white mountain made entirely of giant sushi rice. The snow is dotted with vibrant orange fish roe, creating a sparkling effect. Instead of trees, the landscape is populated with oversized, beautifully detailed pieces of sushi: towering salmon nigiri, California rolls forming gentle hills, and avocado maki rolls standing like charming shrubs. The couple is in mid-action, laughing, with the woman playfully throwing a snowball-sized dollop of wasabi. They are wearing stylish, colorful snowboard gear. The sky is a pastel swirl of pink and lavender clouds, with a few edamame beans floating gently like whimsical balloons. In the center, in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script, the text reads "Happy Birthday, Jordan". The overall aesthetic is flat 2D vector art, full of charm and vibrant colors.
